<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="508" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1437,151,573]" pageId="7" pageNumber="508">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,511,537]" pageId="7" pageNumber="508">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific epithet is derived from the Latin 
<emphasis box="[871,966,511,537]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="508">robustus</emphasis>
and the term 
<emphasis box="[1129,1185,511,536]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="508">juxta</emphasis>
, referring to the stout juxta.
</paragraph>
